item.title: US-101 North at WA-8 West Exit
item.description: US-101 north to Shelton and Port Angeles at WA-8 west to Montesano and Aberdeen.

item.title: US-101 North Approaching WA-8 Exit
item.description: US-101 north approaching WA-8 west. Use WA-8 West for Ocean Beaches. Use US-101 North for Olympic Peninsula.

item.title: US-101 North Approaching WA-8
item.description: US-101 north approaching WA-8 junction. Overhead for US-101 North/Shelton/Port Angeles. US-101 north traffic needs to exit.

item.title: US-12 East Offramp at WA-8
item.description: US-12 east at US-12 offramp. Turn right for US-12 to Oakville and Centralia.

item.title: US-12 East/WA-8 Split
item.description: US-12 east at WA-8. WA-8 traffic continues straight. US-12 East exits here towards Oakville and Centralia.

item.title: I-5 Directions at US-12/WA-8 Split
item.description: US-12 east approaching WA-8. For I-5 north traffic use WA-8 east. For I-5 south use US-12 east.

item.title: US-12 East Approaching US-12/WA-8 Split
item.description: US-12 East approaching WA-8 (unsigned). US-12 traffic must exit.
